<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM.4.4.7">
<l>ēṟiya pittiṉō ṭellā vulakuṅkaṇ ṇaṉpaṭaip peṉṉu</l>
<l>nīṟucev vēyiṭak kāṇi ṉeṭumā laṭiyā reṉṟōṭu</l>
<l>nāṟu tuḻāymalar kāṇi ṉāraṇaṉ kaṇṇiyī teṉṉun</l>
<l>tēṟiyun tēṟātu māyōṉ ṟiṟattaṉa ḷēyit tiruvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the infatuation risen [in her] she says “all the world is Kaṇṇaṉ’s creation”,</l>
<l>when she sees ashes applied correctly she runs, saying “the servants of tall Māl”,</l>
<l>when she sees fragrant Tulsi blossoms she says “this [is] Nāraṇaṉ’s garland”,</l>
<l>believing or not this brilliant [one] has opened to the Dark one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
